metadata.name: Miss Bitcoin
metadata.description: She has been striving to spread Bitcoin around the world since 2011, leading to her nickname “MissBitcoin” both domestically and internationally, and has developed strong connections with global projects. Since 2018, she hosts the world's largest NFT-focused event every year. She serves as an advisor for domestic and overseas projects, including Animoca Brands, and is an angel investor in Sky Mavis, Yield Guild Games, and others.
